[05:48.36]	That I might so have rated my expense,
[05:51.23]	As I had leave of means?
[05:53.19]FLAVIUS	You would not hear me,
[05:55.02]	At many leisures I proposed.
[05:57.23]TIMON	Go to:
[05:58.02]	Perchance some single vantages you took.
[06:01.02]	When my indisposition put you back:
[06:03.69]	And that unaptness made your minister,
[06:06.56]	Thus to excuse yourself.
[06:08.52]FLAVIUS	O my good lord,
[06:09.89]	At many times I brought in my accounts,
[06:12.82]	Laid them before you; you would throw them off,
[06:16.21]	And say, you found them in mine honesty.
[06:19.15]	When, for some trifling present, you have bid me
